com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services

Interface ChangeRecordService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultChangeRecordService

    public interface ChangeRecordService

    The service lets external applications to integrate with sales order processing in SAP S/4 HANA Cloud. This service enables you to retrieve change records in an API call. You can apply any of the filters provided or retrieve all existing data.

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_CHANGE_RECORD
    API Version:1
    Communication Scenario:Product Lifecycle Management - Master Data Integration (SAP_COM_0105)
    Scope Items:Engineering Bill of Material Change Master Management (1R3)
